    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, that's a good start for the pro-density side. But I'm worried about the pushback from long-time residents. A lot of people argue that these high-density projects just drive up property taxes and force out the people who have lived there for decades through gentrification. How do you address that argument?",
